    <h1>BN Identities </h1>
    <!-- InstanceEndEditable -->
      <!-- InstanceBeginEditable name="PageContent" -->
      <p>Bombness Network Identities provide our members a secure way of signing in to Bombness Networks Services. Our consistent sign-in interface makes it simple for anyone to log in - and our simplified sign-up process gives users an easy three-step process to subscribe to the site. At the same time, Bombness Networks maintains a high quality of subscribers through a double opt-in which all members are required to perform in order to take full advantage of the network's services. </p>
      <table width="100%"  border="0" cellpadding="8" cellspacing="0" bordercolor="#666666" bgcolor="#FFFFE8" style="border: 1px solid;">
        <tr>
          <td><a href="login.asp">Users, click here to manage your Bombness Networks Identity &raquo;</a> </td>
        </tr>
      </table><br>
      <table width="400" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="5" style="border: 1px solid #CCCCCC;">
        <tr bgcolor="#EBE9ED">
          <td colspan="2"><strong>Bombness Networks Signup Flow </strong></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td width="20" align="center" valign="middle" bgcolor="#EBE9ED"><div align="center">1</div></td>
          <td bgcolor="#F3F2F4">User completes the sign-up form</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td width="20" align="center" valign="middle" bgcolor="#EBE9ED"><div align="center">2</div></td>
          <td bgcolor="#F3F2F4">User receives an e-mail from Bombness Networks with a confirmation link </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td width="20" align="center" valign="middle" bgcolor="#EBE9ED"><div align="center">3</div></td>
          <td bgcolor="#F3F2F4">User enters their password on the confirmation page after following the confirmation link </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <p>Identities are being implemented on all Bombness Networks sites Members will utilize their identities to uniquely customize their experience on each of them.</p>
      <p><strong>Security Features</strong></p>
      <p>By default, Bombness Network identies can not be signed in at more than one place. Upon signing in on another site or computer, the user will be logged out of any other sites he or she is logged in to. The user can disable this security precaution from their Identity Control Panel. In addition, all passwords are double-hashed using a secure algorithm on our servers. It is virtually impossible to retrieve a password from our servers. In the event of a forgotten password, a password reset link can be sent to your registered e-mail address. The Password Reset wizard will ask for some personal information that must be correct before proceeding. Users are notified by e-mail of any password change on their account. Therefore, it is in every user's best interest to keep their e-mail account secure, as e-mail is used as the primary medium of verification.</p>
      <p><strong>Subscriber and Advertiser Benefits</strong></p>
      <p>Our quality of advertisers is ensured using the double opt-in method. Users willingly and voluntarily subscribe to one or more of our services. We do not purchase members from third parties. All our users are ours. The subscriber benefits from our strict anti-spam policy. We only send e-mail in congruence with our terms of service which every user agrees with at signup. We may send sponsored e-mail messages from time to time. </p>
